  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your mystic connection with one type of wilderness has grown even stronger.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Attuned to the Wild, Guardian of the Wild, elf.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you are in a terrain type you have selected the Attuned to the Wild feat for, you gain a +4 bonus on Perception checks made to act in the surprise round of combat. If you act in the surprise round, you gain blindsense out to a range of 30 feet during the surprise round. If you are in an area that qualifies as more than one kind of terrain, these bonuses do not stack; you receive the bonus for only one terrain type.",
